        "# Función lfybus: Genera la matrix de admitancias de las Barras\n",
        "nl = linedata[:,0].astype(int)\n",
        "nr = linedata[:,1].astype(int)\n",
        "R = linedata[:,2]\n",
        "X = linedata[:,3] * 1j\n",
        "Bc = linedata[:,4] * 1j\n",
        "a = linedata[:,5]\n",
        "nbr = int(len(linedata[:, 0]))\n",
        "nbus = int(max(max(nl), max(nr)))\n",
        "# Matriz de Amitancias\n",
        "Z = R + X\n",
        "Y = ones(nbr) / Z\n",
        "\n",
        "a[a <= 0] = 1\n",
        "\n",
        "Ybus = zeros((nbus, nbus), dtype=complex)\n",
        "for k in range(nbr):\n",
        "    Ybus[nl[k] - 1, nr[k] - 1] -= Y[k] / a[k]\n",
        "    Ybus[nr[k] - 1, nl[k] - 1] = Ybus[nl[k] - 1, nr[k] - 1]\n",
        "\n",
        "for n in range(1, nbus + 1):\n",
        "    for k in range(nbr):\n",
        "        if nl[k] == n:\n",
        "            Ybus[n - 1, n - 1] += Y[k] / (a[k]**2) + Bc[k]\n",
        "        elif nr[k] == n:\n",
        "            Ybus[n - 1, n - 1] += Y[k] + Bc[k]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Función lfnewton: Solución de Flujo de Carga por método Newton Raphson\n",
        "nbus = int(len(busdata[:,0]))\n",
        "\n",
        "ns = 0 #Número de Barras Slack\n",
        "ng = 0 #Número de Generadores / Compensadores Síncronos\n",
        "Vm = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "delta = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "yload = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=complex)\n",
        "deltad = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "\n",
        "kb = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=int)\n",
        "Pd = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qd = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Pg = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qg = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qmin = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qmax = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qsh = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "V = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=complex)\n",
        "P = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Q = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "S = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=complex)\n",
        "\n",
        "for k in range(nbus):\n",
        "    n = int(busdata[k, 0]) - 1  # Restar 1 para índices basados en 0\n",
        "    kb[n] = int(busdata[k, 1]) # Código de Tipo de Barra\n",
        "    Vm[n] = busdata[k, 2]\n",
        "    delta[n] = busdata[k, 3]\n",
        "    Pd[n] = busdata[k, 4]\n",
        "    Qd[n] = busdata[k, 5]\n",
        "    Pg[n] = busdata[k, 6]\n",
        "    Qg[n] = busdata[k, 7]\n",
        "    Qmin[n] = busdata[k, 8]\n",
        "    Qmax[n] = busdata[k, 9]\n",
        "    Qsh[n] = busdata[k, 10]\n",
        "    if Vm[n] <= 0:\n",
        "        Vm[n] = 1.0\n",
        "        V[n] = 1 + 0j\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        delta[n] = np.pi / 180 * delta[n]\n",
        "        V[n] = Vm[n] * (np.cos(delta[n]) + 1j * np.sin(delta[n]))\n",
        "        P[n] = (Pg[n] - Pd[n]) / basemva\n",
        "        Q[n] = (Qg[n] - Qd[n] + Qsh[n]) / basemva\n",
        "        S[n] = P[n] + 1j * Q[n]\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "ngs = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=int) # Guarda el número de Generadores\n",
        "nss = np.zeros(nbus, dtype=int) # Guarda el número de Barras Slack\n",
        "\n",
        "for k in range(nbus):\n",
        "    if kb[k] == 1:\n",
        "        ns += 1\n",
        "    if kb[k] == 2:\n",
        "        ng += 1\n",
        "    ngs[k] = ng\n",
        "    nss[k] = ns\n",
        "\n",
        "Ym = np.abs(Ybus)\n",
        "t = np.angle(Ybus)\n",
        "m = 2*nbus - ng - 2*ns # Tamaño de la Matriz Jacobiana\n",
        "maxerror = 1\n",
        "converge = 1\n",
        "iter_ = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "A = np.zeros((m, m))\n",
        "DC = np.zeros(m)\n",
        "J = np.zeros((m, m))\n",
        "DX = np.zeros(m)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Inicio de iteraciones\n",
        "while maxerror >= accuracy and iter_ <= maxiter:\n",
        "    # Inicialización de la matriz Jacobiana\n",
        "    A = np.zeros((m, m))\n",
        "\n",
        "    iter_ += 1\n",
        "\n",
        "    for n in range(nbus):# Desde 0 hasta (nbus-1)\n",
        "        nn = (n+1) - nss[n] - 1\n",
        "        lm = nbus + (n+1) - ngs[n] - nss[n] - ns - 1\n",
        "        J11 = J22 = J33 = J44 = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "        for i in range(nbr):# Desde 0 hasta (nbr-1)\n",
        "            if nl[i] == (n + 1) or nr[i] == (n + 1):\n",
        "                if nl[i] == (n+1):\n",
        "                    l = nr[i] - 1\n",
        "                if nr[i] == (n+1):\n",
        "                    l = nl[i] - 1\n",
        "\n",
        "                J11 += Vm[n] * Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.sin(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                J33 += Vm[n] * Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.cos(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                if kb[n] != 1:\n",
        "                    J22 += Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.cos(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                    J44 += Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.sin(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "\n",
        "                if kb[n] != 1 and kb[l] != 1:\n",
        "                    lk = nbus + (l+1) - ngs[l] - nss[l] - ns -1\n",
        "                    ll = (l+1) - nss[l] - 1\n",
        "\n",
        "                    A[nn, ll] = -Vm[n] * Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.sin(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                    if kb[l] == 0:\n",
        "                        A[nn, lk] = Vm[n] * Ym[n, l] * np.cos(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                    if kb[n] == 0:\n",
        "                        A[lm, ll] = -Vm[n] * Vm[l] * Ym[n, l] * np.cos(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "                    if kb[n] == 0 and kb[l] == 0:\n",
        "                        A[lm, lk] = -Vm[n] * Ym[n, l] * np.sin(t[n, l] - delta[n] + delta[l])\n",
        "        Pk = Vm[n]**2 * Ym[n, n] * np.cos(t[n, n]) + J33\n",
        "        Qk = -Vm[n]**2 * Ym[n, n] * np.sin(t[n, n]) - J11\n",
        "\n",
        "        if kb[n] == 1: # Para la Barra Slack\n",
        "            P[n] = Pk\n",
        "            Q[n] = Qk\n",
        "\n",
        "        if kb[n] == 2: # Para la Barra de Tensión Controlada (PV)\n",
        "            Q[n] = Qk\n",
        "            if Qmax[n] != 0:\n",
        "                Qgc = Q[n] * basemva + Qd[n] - Qsh[n]\n",
        "                if iter_ <= 7:\n",
        "                    if iter_ > 2: # Entre la 2da y 7ma iteración verifica los límites de Potencia Reactiva\n",
        "                        if Qgc < Qmin[n]:\n",
        "                            Vm[n] += 0.01\n",
        "                        elif Qgc > Qmax[n]:\n",
        "                            Vm[n] -= 0.01\n",
        "\n",
        "        if kb[n] != 1: # Para los que NO son Barra Slack\n",
        "            A[nn, nn] = J11\n",
        "            DC[nn] = P[n] - Pk\n",
        "\n",
        "        if kb[n] == 0: # Para las barras de Carga (PQ)\n",
        "            A[nn, lm] = 2 * Vm[n] * Ym[n, n] * np.cos(t[n, n]) + J22\n",
        "            A[lm, nn] = J33\n",
        "            A[lm, lm] = -2 * Vm[n] * Ym[n, n] * np.sin(t[n, n]) - J44\n",
        "            DC[lm] = Q[n] - Qk\n",
        "\n",
        "    DX = np.linalg.solve(A, DC)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for n in range(nbus):\n",
        "        nn = (n+1) - nss[n] - 1\n",
        "        lm = nbus + (n+1) - ngs[n] - nss[n] - ns - 1\n",
        "\n",
        "        if kb[n] != 1: # Para los que NO son Barra Slack\n",
        "            delta[n] += DX[nn]\n",
        "        if kb[n] == 0: # Para las barras de Carga (PQ)\n",
        "            Vm[n] += DX[lm]\n",
        "\n",
        "    maxerror = np.max(np.abs(DC))\n",
        "\n",
        "    if iter_ == maxiter and maxerror > accuracy:\n",
        "        print(f'\\nADVERTENCIA: La solución no convergió después de : {iter_} iteraciones.\\n\\n')\n",
        "        converge = 0\n",
        "        break\n",
        "\n",
        "if converge != 1:\n",
        "    print('EL RESULTADO ITERATIVO NO CONVERGE')\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print('Solución de Flujo de Potencia por Método de Newton-Raphson\\n')\n",
        "\n",
        "V = Vm * np.cos(delta) + 1j * Vm * np.sin(delta)\n",
        "deltad = 180 / np.pi * delta\n",
        "i = 1j\n",
        "k = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "Pgg = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "Qgg = np.zeros(nbus)\n",
        "\n",
        "for n in range(nbus):\n",
        "    if kb[n] == 1:\n",
        "        k += 1\n",
        "        S[n] = P[n] + 1j * Q[n]\n",
        "        Pg[n] = P[n] * basemva + Pd[n]\n",
        "        Qg[n] = Q[n] * basemva + Qd[n] - Qsh[n]\n",
        "        Pgg[k] = Pg[n]\n",
        "        Qgg[k] = Qg[n]\n",
        "    elif kb[n] == 2:\n",
        "        k += 1\n",
        "        S[n] = P[n] + 1j * Q[n]\n",
        "        Qg[n] = Q[n] * basemva + Qd[n] - Qsh[n]\n",
        "        Pgg[k] = Pg[n]\n",
        "        Qgg[k] = Qg[n]\n",
        "\n",
        "    yload[n] = (Pd[n] - 1j * Qd[n] + 1j * Qsh[n]) / (basemva * Vm[n] ** 2)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "busdata[:, 2] = Vm\n",
        "busdata[:, 3] = deltad\n",
        "Pgt = np.sum(Pg)\n",
        "Qgt = np.sum(Qg)\n",
        "Pdt = np.sum(Pd)\n",
        "Qdt = np.sum(Qd)\n",
        "Qsht = np.sum(Qsh)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Función busout: Imprime la solución del Flujo de Potencia\n",
        "\n",
        "# Imprimir el resultado de la convergencia\n",
        "print(f'                                 Máximo error de la Potencia = {maxerror:.6f}')\n",
        "print(f'                                              Número de Iteraciones = {iter_:d}\\n')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Encabezado de la tabla\n",
        "encabezado = ('''\n",
        "Nro    Magnitud  Ang       ----Carga-----      --Generador---    Inyect.\n",
        "Barra  Tensión   Grados    MW        MVAR      MW        MVAR    MVar\n",
        "''')\n",
        "print(encabezado)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Imprimir los resultados de cada bus\n",
        "for n in range(nbus):\n",
        "    print(f' {n+1:3d} {Vm[n]:7.3f} {deltad[n]:8.3f} {Pd[n]:9.3f} {Qd[n]:9.3f} {Pg[n]:9.3f} {Qg[n]:9.3f} {Qsh[n]:8.3f}')\n",
        "\n",
        "print('      \\n')\n",
        "print(f'Total                {Pdt:9.3f} {Qdt:9.3f} {Pgt:9.3f} {Qgt:9.3f} {Qsht:9.3f}\\n')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Función lineflow: Calcula y muestra el Flujo de Potencia y Pérdidas\n",
        "\n",
        "SLT = 0\n",
        "print('\\n')\n",
        "print('                           Flujo en Lineas y Pérdidas\\n')\n",
        "print('     ---Linea----    Flujo de Potencia Barra o Linea    --Pérdidas de Linea--  tap del')\n",
        "print('     desde  hasta     MW         Mvar       MVA         MW         Mvar        transformador')\n",
        "\n",
        "for n in range(nbus):# Desde 0 hasta (nbus-1)\n",
        "    busprt = 0\n",
        "    for L in range(nbr):# Desde 0 hasta (nbr-1)\n",
        "        if busprt == 0:\n",
        "            print(f'   \\n{n+1:6d}      {P[n] * basemva:16.3f}{Q[n] * basemva:11.3f}{abs(S[n] * basemva):11.3f}')\n",
        "            busprt = 1\n",
        "        if nl[L] == (n + 1):\n",
        "            k = nr[L] - 1\n",
        "            In = (V[n] - a[L] * V[k]) * Y[L] / a[L]**2 + Bc[L] / a[L]**2 * V[n]\n",
        "            Ik = (V[k] - V[n] / a[L]) * Y[L] + Bc[L] * V[k]\n",
        "            Snk = V[n] * np.conj(In) * basemva\n",
        "            Skn = V[k] * np.conj(Ik) * basemva\n",
        "            SL = Snk + Skn\n",
        "            SLT += SL\n",
        "        elif nr[L] == (n + 1):\n",
        "            k = nl[L] - 1\n",
        "            In = (V[n] - V[k] / a[L]) * Y[L] + Bc[L] * V[n]\n",
        "            Ik = (V[k] - a[L] * V[n]) * Y[L] / a[L]**2 + Bc[L] / a[L]**2 * V[k]\n",
        "            Snk = V[n] * np.conj(In) * basemva\n",
        "            Skn = V[k] * np.conj(Ik) * basemva\n",
        "            SL = Snk + Skn\n",
        "            SLT += SL\n",
        "        if nl[L] == (n + 1) or nr[L] == (n + 1):\n",
        "            print(f'{k+1:14d}{np.real(Snk):14.3f}{np.imag(Snk):11.3f}{np.abs(Snk):11.3f}{np.real(SL):11.3f}', end='')\n",
        "            if nl[L] == (n + 1) and a[L] != 1:\n",
        "                print(f'{np.imag(SL):11.3f}{a[L]:12.3f}')\n",
        "            else:\n",
        "                print(f'{np.imag(SL):11.3f}')\n",
        "\n",
        "SLT = SLT / 2\n",
        "print('   \\n    Total loss                         ', end='')\n",
        "print(f'{np.real(SLT):22.3f}{np.imag(SLT):11.3f}')"
